supposed to be helping your
father right about now?

37
00:03:54,125 --> 00:03:55,541
No, not really.

38
00:03:55,625 --> 00:04:00,000
And to tell you the truth,
I just came to see Leon Oswald.

39
00:04:00,083 --> 00:04:01,666
Oh, of course.

40
00:04:01,750 --> 00:04:03,833
He is the prince
of the French circus,

41
00:04:03,916 --> 00:04:05,500
the Pegasus of the stage.

42
00:04:05,583 --> 00:04:08,208
The most talented performer
in the whole world!

43
00:04:08,291 --> 00:04:09,541
But no one knows his past...

44
00:04:09,625 --> 00:04:11,500
He's so mysterious.

45
00:04:11,583 --> 00:04:13,583
There's no time
for this conversation.

46
00:04:13,666 --> 00:04:14,916
This is the first day

47
