she can draw an
audience by herself.

50
00:04:19,375 --> 00:04:21,875
Sora! Where could you be?

51
00:04:21,958 --> 00:04:23,833
I found her.

52
00:04:23,916 --> 00:04:25,166
Look!

53
00:04:26,625 --> 00:04:27,208
What?

54
00:04:27,291 --> 00:04:28,791
What is she doing?

55
00:04:28,875 --> 00:04:31,750
With Layla gone, we've lost
some of our audience, so...

56
00:04:31,833 --> 00:04:32,958
I think Sora's trying

57
00:04:33,041 --> 00:04:35,083
to win them back by
advertising the show.

58
00:04:35,166 --> 00:04:36,000
Uh, dang it!

59
00:04:37,958 --> 00:04:39,583
I'm going too!

60
00:04:39,666 --> 00:04:40,791
Please don't, Anna!

61
00:04:40,875 --> 00:04:42,375
So I can't go?

62
00:04:47,416 --> 00:04:50,208
Everybody!
Kaleido Stage is fun!

63
00:04:50,291 --> 00:04:51,416
So come-

64
